OL,3,CSub-postmistress's fear becomes
OL,4,Creality as she dies before
OL,5,Ccompensation payout
OL,7,FA former sub-post mistress who gave
OL,8,Fher savings to the Post Office and
OL,9,Fborrowed money to make up for
OL,10,Fshortfalls created by the Horizon IT
OL,11,Fsystem has died without receiving
OL,12,Fcompensation.
OL,14,FCarol Riddell, who ran the post office
OL,15,Fin East Boldon, near Sunderland, with
OL,16,Fher husband Alan, had told him she was
OL,17,Fafraid she would die before the matter
OL,18,Fwas resolved.
