OL,4,Creality as she dies before
OL,5,Ccompensation payout
OL,7,FShe is one of a growing number of
OL,8,Fformer sub-postmasters and sub-
OL,9,Fpostmistresses to die amid delays to
OL,10,Fthe compensation.
OL,12,FOn Tuesday (5 November) a panel of MPs
OL,13,Fheard from those at the centre of the
OL,14,FPost Office Horizon scandal as to why
OL,15,Fit has taken so long for some of the
OL,16,Fvictims to receive compensation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/13
