OL,5,Ccompensation payout
OL,7,FSpeaking of his late wife, Alan
OL,8,FRiddell told ITV Tyne Tees: "She said
OL,9,F'I'll be dead before this is sorted'
OL,10,Fand it's come to fruition. It's hard
OL,11,Fthat she's never going to see her
OL,12,Fredress. She'll never see the
OL,13,Fgrandkids grow up. It's terrible what
OL,14,Fthey've done, not just to us but all
OL,15,Fpost masters."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/13
