OL,7,FHe added: "They're hoping everyone is
OL,8,Fgoing to be dead before they have to
OL,9,Fgive us money. They offer a paltry
OL,10,Famount and they know you're going to
OL,11,Fsay no. It's just going to go on and
OL,12,Fon and on. Nothing changes."
OL,14,FMrs Riddell took over the post office
OL,15,Fin 1992 but things started going wrong
OL,16,Fafter the Horizon IT system was
OL,17,Fintroduced in 1999.
