OL,7,FPrior to her death, she gave a
OL,8,Fstatement to the Horizon inquiry
OL,9,Fsaying she had been threatened with
OL,10,Fprosecution several times over
OL,11,Frepeated shortfalls - leading to
OL,12,Fstress and anxiety.
OL,14,FMr Riddell, who took over the post
OL,15,Foffice in 2000, was eventually
OL,16,Fsuspended from his position and had to
OL,17,Fattend a disciplinary hearing over the
OL,18,Fissue.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/13
