OL,7,FJean Smith, who was a friend of Mrs
OL,8,FRiddell's, told ITV Tyne Tees: "I can
OL,9,Fstill remember the day they moved. She
OL,10,Fwas so excited about it and to think
OL,11,Fthat dream was turned upside down and
OL,12,Fbecame a nightmare is just so hard."
OL,14,FA friend of more than 40 years, Jean
OL,15,Fstepped in to help when the stress was
OL,16,Ftoo much.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/13
