OL,7,F"Carol was the kindest, loveliest lady
OL,8,Fand for her to feel so much anger, and
OL,9,Fthe word never used - hate - towards
OL,10,Fthe Post Office was hard," she
OL,11,Fcontinued. "It absolutely broke her."
OL,13,FAlan Bates, who has been giving
OL,14,Fevidence today at a Business and Trade
OL,15,FCommittee hearing on the Horizon
OL,16,Fscandal, told ITV News a growing
OL,17,Fnumber of people are dying while
OL,18,Fawaiting compensation. He also said
OL,19,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer had
OL,20,Fignored two letters regarding ongoing
OL,21,Fdelays to compensation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/13
