OL,7,FAlso giving evidence to the panel of
OL,8,FMPs, who are looking into the
OL,9,Fcompensation delays, was Jill Donnison.
OL,11,FHer late mother Janet ran a post
OL,12,Foffice in Horden. She has applied for
OL,13,Fcompensation through the Horizon
OL,14,FShortfall Scheme, something she
OL,15,Fdescribed as "not very user friendly".
OL,17,FThere are four schemes people can
OL,18,Fapply for redress through, two of
OL,19,Fwhich the Post Office is directly
OL,20,Finvolved with, including the Horizon
OL,21,FShortfall Scheme.
