OL,7,FA Post Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Fstrongly encourage eligible former and
OL,9,Fcurrent postmasters to come forward
OL,10,Fand claim redress. Post Office is
OL,11,Fcommitted to doing all it can to
OL,12,Fensure that all victims of the scandal
OL,13,Freceive the financial redress they
OL,14,Fdeserve and to providing this as
OL,15,Fquickly as possible."
