OL,7,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Frecognise the immeasurable suffering
OL,9,Fpostmasters have endured and
OL,10,Funderstand their frustration after
OL,11,Fyears of inaction and delay. But this
OL,12,FGovernment is working tirelessly to
OL,13,Fprovide full, fair and swift redress.
OL,15,F"The amount of redress paid has nearly
OL,16,Fdoubled under this government with
OL,17,Fmore claims being resolved quickly;
OL,18,F#438m has now been paid to 3,100
OL,19,Fclaimants.
